{"title":"心的锚链","authors":["于尊业"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":12,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"心的锚链"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟台印刷厂  于尊业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在海员的帽徽上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一支闪光的锚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它始终向下垂着——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可知是起锚还是落锚？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我敢说，每个海员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对这个问题他都想到；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起锚——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就让生命的航船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓起风帆奔向明朝；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落锚——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就让心的锚钩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把海底的礁石紧紧抓牢……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辞别家乡，踏波远航，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锚链系着妻子的叮咛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小女儿银铃般的笑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它短吗？不呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心的锚链，穿过茫茫碧波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把祖国的码头紧紧拥抱……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}